
---


@startuml

' Define classes
class Employee {
    + String name
    + String role
}

class HeadCoach {
    + identifyDesignatedPlayerProfiles()
    + setTargetPositions()
    + addPlayerAttributes()
}

class Director {
    + makeOfficialOffer()
}

class Scout {
    + notePlayerOnLongList()
    + submitScoutingReport()
    + evaluateProsAndCons()
    + giveRecommendation()
}

class HeadScout {
    + evaluateLongList()
    + assignScoutingAssignments()
    + decideShortlist()
}

class DesignatedPlayerProfile {
    + String position
    + List<PlayerAttribute> attributes
}

class PlayerAttribute {
    + String attributeName
    + String attributeValue
}

class Player {
    + String name
    + String position
    + List<ScoutingReport> reports
}

class LongList {}

class ShortList {}

class ScoutingAssignment {
    + Date startDate
    + Date endDate
    + Player player
    + Scout assignedScout
}

class ScoutingReport {
    + String pros
    + String cons
    + Recommendation recommendation
}

enum Recommendation {
    KeyPlayer
    FirstTeamPlayer
    ReserveTeamPlayer
    ProspectivePlayer
    NotAGoodSigning
}

' Inheritance
Employee <|-- HeadCoach
Employee <|-- Director
Employee <|-- Scout
Employee <|-- HeadScout

' Associations
HeadCoach --> "1" DesignatedPlayerProfile : creates
DesignatedPlayerProfile --> "0..*" PlayerAttribute : has
Scout --> "0..*" ScoutingReport : submits
Scout --> "0..*" ScoutingAssignment : performs
HeadScout --> "1" LongList : evaluates
HeadScout --> "0..*" ScoutingAssignment : assigns
ScoutingAssignment --> "1" Player : targets
ScoutingAssignment --> "1" Scout : assigned to
ScoutingReport --> "1" ScoutingAssignment : part of
Player --> "0..*" ScoutingReport : has
LongList --> "0..*" Player : contains
ShortList --> "0..*" Player : contains
Director --> "1" Player : makes offer for

@enduml

---

### 📌 Notes:
- The system includes roles (`HeadCoach`, `Director`, `Scout`, `HeadScout`) all extending from an abstract `Employee` class.
- A `DesignatedPlayerProfile` defines what kind of players are being targeted by the club.
- Players can be in either a `LongList` or a `ShortList`.
- `ScoutingAssignment` links a `Scout` to a `Player`, and each assignment leads to a `ScoutingReport`.
- `ScoutingReport` includes the scout’s evaluation and recommendation for a player.

